OL,3,CHouseholds could face 8% jump in food
OL,4,Cprices due to Iran war, experts warn
OL,6,FUK households could face food
OL,7,Finflation above 8% within months if
OL,8,Fdisruption caused by the Iran war
OL,9,Fpersists, grocery industry experts
OL,10,Fhave warned.
OL,12,FIGD (Institute of Grocery
OL,13,FDistribution) said the conflict in the
OL,14,FMiddle East could result in food
OL,15,Finflation more than doubling by the
OL,16,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
