OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774444274
OL,3,CHouseholds could face 8% jump in food
OL,4,Cprices due to Iran war, experts warn
OL,6,FFresh forecasts by the organisation
OL,7,Fshow that food inflation could
OL,8,Fincrease from its current rate of 3.6%
OL,9,Fto "briefly reach over 8% by June
OL,10,F2026", if firms are impacted by "most
OL,11,Fsevere but short-lived energy shock
OL,12,Fscenario".
OL,14,FThe predicted acceleration comes after
OL,15,Fa sustained period of rising food and
OL,16,Fdrink prices for UK households.
OL,26,@qD@DOUrD@EO]rD@aOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
