OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774444274
OL,3,CHouseholds could face 8% jump in food
OL,4,Cprices due to Iran war, experts warn
OL,6,FUK retail food prices are now around
OL,7,F38% higher than pre-Covid levels, with
OL,8,Fthe energy price surges following the
OL,9,FRussian invasion of Ukraine
OL,10,Fparticularly contributing to rises
OL,11,Fover the period.
OL,13,FIGD said its highest impact scenario
OL,14,Fwould see a "short-lived but severe"
OL,15,Fincrease in food prices, with
OL,16,Finflation rising to around 6.4% across
OL,17,F2026 as a result.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
