OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774444274
OL,3,CHouseholds could face 8% jump in food
OL,4,Cprices due to Iran war, experts warn
OL,6,F"Our analysis shows that the evidence
OL,7,Fpoints in the opposite direction:
OL,8,Fmargins for basic food and drink
OL,9,Fremain exceptionally thin, and in many
OL,10,Fcases have fallen in recent years.
OL,12,F"When margins are this tight,
OL,13,Fbusinesses have limited capacity to
OL,14,Fabsorb global shocks, invest in
OL,15,Fresilience or protect supply.
OL,17,F"Over time, that increases the risk of
OL,18,Fweaker availability and greater price
OL,19,Fvolatility."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
